She's got as many eyes as a potato . 
I can ! I said firmly . 
Well , I stood in the doorway and watched them disappear in the darkness , and I felt better than I had all day . 
It's great to be able to DO something , even if that something is wrong . 
But as I put on my shawl and turned out the lights , I suddenly remembered . 
Miss Patty would be waiting in the lobby for Mr. Dick , and she would not be crocheting ! CHAPTER VII . 
PIERCE ACQUIRES A WIFE Whoever has charge of the spring house at Hope Springs takes the news stand in the evening . 
The news stand includes tobacco and a circulating library , and is close to the office , and if I missed any human nature at the spring I got it there . 
