Thoburn's idea , of course , is to make the guests discontented , so they will leave . 
She hadn't thought of that , and she flushed . 
At least , she said , you must give me credit for not trying to spoil Dick and Dolly's chance here . 
We are going to allow the party to go on , he said , still stiff and uncompromising . 
It would have been better if he'd accepted her bit of apology . 
How kind of you ! I dare say he would have it , anyhow . 
And you will go ? Certainly . 
Even when the result Oh , don't preach ! she said , putting her hands to her ears . 
