He stopped and eyed her back , but she did not move . 
It is impertinence under any circumstances , but consider the provocation . 
It must be a long sermon . 
And then , knowing he had only a moment more , his voice changed and became deep and earnest . 
His hands , that were clutching a chair back , took a stronger hold , so that the ends of the nails were white . 
